## 🔐 Security Considerations

- Service offers are immutable on blockchain (can't be secretly modified)
- Payment required before service delivery (edge node verifies on blockchain)
- Edge node authentication required
- Offer reservation prevents double-booking

## 📈 Performance Targets

- Offer registration: <1s (blockchain transaction)
- Offer discovery: <100ms (RPC query)
- Match: <200ms
- Edge node serving start: <500ms (after payment confirmation)
- Payment confirmation: <2s (block inclusion)

